Client Code *: At least one of Client Code or Client Name is required; Max 20 chars
Client Name *: At least one of Client Code or Client Name is required; Case Sensitive and Max 200 chars
Date Purchased *: If this field is left blank you must select to ignore invalid Date Purchased on import to import blank values.
Serial Number *: If you wish to import serial numbers for Equipment enter them in this field (must be unique)
Value: If you need to import data for custom fields specify the name of custom field in column header. Remove column if there are no custom fields.
Year commissioned: If you need to import data for custom fields specify the name of custom field in column header. Remove column if there are no custom fields.
